nodes.text: Interstellar garden salad was a type of salad served at Dex's Diner on the planet Coruscant. It was the most popular of the salads available on the menu and consisted of crisp revwien lettuce garnished with topatoes, space carrot, qiraadishes, Mandalorian oranges, Sriluurian raisins and Wol Cabasshews and served with luptoomian dressing. It cost 5.7 credits, and for an extra credit grilled gornt meat was added.
